"][img style="width:400px; height:auto;"]https://i.imgur.com/rI7xguA.png[/img]
    [size=25]T[/size]his guide is designed to offer [color=#F7D58B]Paladins[/color] of all levels a comprehensive and streamlined resource. Whether you're new to the role or experienced, this guide centralizes essential knowledge to enhance your gameplay.
    
    While some content may resemble wiki entries, it is enriched with in-depth analysis and practical advice. [color=#F7D58B]Constructive feedback[/color] is always welcome to keep this guide relevant and up-to-date.
    
    [/div]
    
