    [div style="
    margin:0 auto; 
    background-color:rgba(26, 26, 26, 0.85); 
    width:100%; 
    padding:5px; 
    border-radius:15px;
    box-shadow: inset 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 1), 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 1);
    border:3px ridge #F7D58B;"][div align="center" style="margin:15px 0 25px 0; padding:10px;"][img style="width:450px; height:auto;"]https://i.imgur.com/Rd4V1im.png[/img][/div][div id="section-role" style="
        font-size:25px;
        font-family:Garamond, serif;
        font-weight:bold; 
        color: #cea425; text-shadow: 0px 0px 0px rgba(0, 0, 0, 1); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px;"]Enmity[/div]
        [div id="section-paladin-merits" style="
        margin:10px auto; 
        background-color:rgba(254, 254, 254, 0.1); 
        padding:10px; 
        border-radius:10px; 
        border:2px ridge rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5); 
        box-shadow: inset 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 1), 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);  
        color:#E0E0E0; 
        font-size:14px;
        line-height:1.5;
        text-align:left;"][div align="center"][div style="font-size:20px; color: #cea425; text-shadow: 0px 0px 2px 10px #967616;"]Enmity Types & Characteristics[/div]
                [url=#section-enmity-main style="font-size:14px;"][color=#2980B9]▲ Back to top ▲[/color][/url]
                
                
                [div align="center"][table style="width:100%; border:2px ridge rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5); font-size:12px;"]
                        [tr style="background-color:#222222;"]
                            [th style="color:#ffd700; text-align:center; padding:10px; vertical-align:middle; width:33.33%; border:2px ridge rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);"]Enmity Type[/th]
                            [th style="color:#ffd700; text-align:center; padding:10px; vertical-align:middle; width:33.33%; border:2px ridge rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);"]Maximum[/th]
                            [th style="color:#ffd700; text-align:center; padding:10px; vertical-align:middle; width:33.33%; border:2px ridge rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);"]Details[/th]
                        [/tr]
                        [tr style="background-color:#444444;"]
                            [td style="color:#ffa07a; text-align:center; padding:10px; vertical-align:middle; border:2px ridge rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);"]Volatile Enmity (VE)[/td]
                            [td style="color:#ffa07a; text-align:center; padding:10px; vertical-align:middle; border:2px ridge rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);"]30,000[/td]
                            [td style="color:#E0E0E0; text-align:center; padding:10px; vertical-align:middle; border:2px ridge rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);"]• Decay Rate: [color=#ffa07a]-60 VE/sec[/color][/td]
                        [/tr]
                        [tr style="background-color:#333333;"]
                            [td style="color:#ffa366; text-align:center; padding:10px; vertical-align:middle; border:2px ridge rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);"]Cumulative Enmity (CE)[/td]
                            [td style="color:#ffa366; text-align:center; padding:10px; vertical-align:middle; border:2px ridge rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);"]30,000[/td]
                            [td style="color:#E0E0E0; text-align:center; padding:10px; vertical-align:middle; border:2px ridge rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);"]• Formula: ([color=#ffa366]CE[/color] × [color=#d64848]Damage[/color]) ÷ [color=#7fe07f]Max HP[/color][/td]
                        [/tr]
                        [tr style="background-color:#444444;"]
                            [td style="color:#ff4500; text-align:center; padding:10px; vertical-align:middle; border:2px ridge rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);"]Total Enmity (TE)[/td]
                            [td style="color:#ff4500; text-align:center; padding:10px; vertical-align:middle; border:2px ridge rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);"]60,000[/td]
                            [td style="color:#E0E0E0; text-align:center; padding:10px; vertical-align:middle; border:2px ridge rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);"]• Targeting priority = [color=#ffa07a]VE[/color] + [color=#ffa366]CE[/color][/td]
                        [/tr]
                    [/table][/div][/div]
        [/div]

        [div id="section-ce-loss-reduction" style="
        margin:10px auto; 
        background-color:rgba(254, 254, 254, 0.1); 
        padding:10px; 
        border-radius:10px; 
        border:2px ridge rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5); 
        box-shadow: inset 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 1), 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);  
        color:#E0E0E0; 
        font-size:14px;
        line-height:1.5;
        text-align:left;"][div align="center"][div style="font-size:20px; color: #cea425; text-shadow: 0px 0px 2px 10px #967616;"]Optimizing CE loss Reduction with Gear and Enmity+[/div]
                [url=#section-enmity-main style="font-size:14px;"][color=#2980B9]▲ Back to top ▲[/color][/url]
            [/div]
            
            
            [div style="text-align:left"]Managing [color=#ff7f50]Cumulative Enmity (CE)[/color] is crucial for holding aggro, especially in multi-target fights. Reduce [color=#ff7f50]CE loss[/color] through:  
                • [color=#ff7f50]Enmity+[/color] stats.  
                • Gear with [color=#ff7f50]Reduces Enmity Loss[/color].  
                • The bard song [color=#00ffd0]Foe Sirvente[/color].  

                Gear reduction and [color=#00ffd0]Foe Sirvente[/color] stack multiplicatively, allowing up to [color=#ffb380]75% CE loss reduction[/color] when combined.

                [color=#cea425][b]Example[/b][/color]  
                With [color=#ff7f50]+100 Enmity[/color] ([color=#ffb380]50% reduction[/color]) and [color=#00ffd0]Foe Sirvente[/color] + gear ([color=#ffb380]50% reduction[/color]):  
                [color=#ffa366]Total Reduction[/color] = 1 - [(1 - 0.50) × (1 - 0.50)] = [color=#ffb380]75%[/color].  
                You lose only [color=#ffa366]25%[/color] of your [color=#ffa366]CE[/color] when taking damage.

                [color=#cea425][b]Tips[/b][/color]  
                • Prioritize survivability ([color=#ffb380]DT, PDT, MDT[/color]) first.  
                • Use [color=#00ffd0]Foe Sirvente[/color] in fights with multiple enemies.  
                • Balance gear to avoid overcapping [color=#ffa366]CE reduction[/color].
            [/div]


            [table style="width:100%; border:2px ridge rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5); font-size:12px;"]
                    [tr style="background-color:#222222;"]
                        [th colspan="4" style="color:#ffd700; text-align:center; padding:10px; font-size:16px; background-color:#222222;"]Types of CE Loss Reduction[/th]
                    [/tr]
                [tr style="background-color:#222222;"]
                    [th style="color:#ffd700; text-align:center; padding:10px; vertical-align:middle; border:2px ridge rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);"]Source[/th]
                    [th style="color:#ffd700; text-align:center; padding:10px; vertical-align:middle; border:2px ridge rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);"]Max Contribution[/th]
                    [th style="color:#ffd700; text-align:center; padding:10px; vertical-align:middle; border:2px ridge rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);"]Notes[/th]
                [/tr]

                [tr style="background-color:#444444;"]
                    [td style="color:#E0E0E0; text-align:center; padding:10px; vertical-align:middle; border:2px ridge rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);"][color=#ff7f50]Enmity+[/color][/td]
                    [td style="color:#E0E0E0; text-align:center; padding:10px; vertical-align:middle; border:2px ridge rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);"][color=#ff7f50]50%[/color][/td]
                    [td style="color:#E0E0E0; text-align:center; padding:10px; vertical-align:middle; border:2px ridge rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);"]1% reduction per +2 Enmity, capped at +100 Enmity.[/td]
                [/tr]

                [tr style="background-color:#333333;"]
                    [td style="color:#E0E0E0; text-align:center; padding:10px; vertical-align:middle; border:2px ridge rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);"][color=#ffb380]Reduced Enmity Loss (Gear + Foe Sirvente)[/color][/td]
                    [td style="color:#E0E0E0; text-align:center; padding:10px; vertical-align:middle; border:2px ridge rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);"][color=#ffa366]50%[/color][/td]
                    [td style="color:#E0E0E0; padding:10px; vertical-align:middle; text-align:center; border:2px ridge rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);"][div style="text-align:left; margin:0 auto; display:inline-block; width:50%; white-space:normal;"][url=http://www.ffxiah.com/item/20687/burtgang target="\_blank"][img]https://static.ffxiah.com/images/icon/20687.png[/img][/url] [color=#F7D58B]Burtgang[/color] ([color=#ffa366]-20%[/color])

                        [url=http://www.ffxiah.com/item/23627/chevaliers-cuisses-1 target="\_blank"][img]https://static.ffxiah.com/images/icon/23627.png[/img][/url] [color=#F7D58B]Chevalier's Cuisses +3[/color] ([color=#ffa366]-14%[/color])

                        [url=https://www.ffxiah.com/item/11595/creed-collar target="\_blank"][img]https://static.ffxiah.com/images/icon/11595.png[/img][/url] [color=#F7D58B]Creed Collar[/color] ([color=#ffa366]-5%[/color])

                        [url=https://www.bg-wiki.com/ffxi/Foe_Sirvente target="\_blank"][img]https://www.bg-wiki.com/images/1/17/Foe_Sirvente_%28Scroll%29_icon.png[/img][/url] [color=#00ffd0]Foe Sirvente[/color]: Adds up to [color=#ffa366]50%[/color] reduction, combined with gear effects. Shares the same cap as gear effects.[/div]
                    [/td]
                [/tr]

                [tr style="background-color:#444444;"]
                    [td colspan="3" style="color:#E0E0E0; text-align:center; padding:10px; vertical-align:middle;"]Maximum Total Reduction: [color=#ffa366]75%[/color]  
                        This is achieved through [color=#f27126]50% Enmity+[/color] and 50% Gear/Foe Sirvente, applied multiplicatively:  
                        [color=#ffa366]Total Reduction[/color] = 1 - [(1 - 0.50) × (1 - 0.50)] = [color=#ffa366]75%[/color].
                    [/td]
                [/tr]
            [/table][/div]

        [div id="section-healing" style="
            margin:10px auto; 
            background-color:rgba(254, 254, 254, 0.1); 
            padding:10px; 
            border-radius:10px; 
            border:2px ridge rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5); 
            box-shadow: inset 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 1), 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);  
            color:#E0E0E0; 
            font-size:14px;
            line-height:1.5;
            text-align:left;"][div align="center" style="text-align:center; font-size:25px;"][color=#cea425]Enmity Generated by Healing[/color]
                [url=#section-enmity-main style="font-size:14px;"][color=#2980B9]▲ Back to top ▲[/color][/url]
            [/div]
            
            [color=#cea425][b]Simplified Enmity Calculations[/b][/color]
            [color=#ffa366]Cumulative Enmity (CE):[/color]  
            • Formula: [color=#ffa366]CE = [color=#7fe07f]HP Healed[/color]  × [color=#F7D58B]CE Modifier[/color][/color]  
            • For level 99+ enemies, the [color=#F7D58B]CE Modifier[/color] is fixed at [color=#F7D58B]0.231[/color].

            [color=#ffa07a][b]Volatile Enmity (VE):[/b][/color]  
            • Formula: [color=#ffa07a]VE = CE × 6[/color]  

            [color=#cea425][b]Key Adjustments:[/b][/color]  
            • [color=#ffa366]CE[/color] and [color=#ffa07a]VE[/color] are divided by the number of enemies targeting the healer.  
            • [color=#ff7f50]Enmity+[/color] increases [color=#ffa366]CE[/color]; [color=#ff7f50]Enmity-[/color] can reduce it to 0, but the minimum is 1 CE.  

            [color=#cea425][b]Example: Self-Healing Set[/b][/color]  
            • Gear: [color=#ff7f50]Enmity+57[/color], Spell: [color=#00ffd0]Crusade[/color] adds [color=#ff7f50]Enmity+30[/color].  
            • Total: [color=#ff7f50]Enmity+87[/color], increasing both [color=#ffa366]CE[/color] and [color=#ffa07a]VE[/color].

            [color=#cea425][b]Formula Details:[/b][/color]  
            • Base CE = [color=#7fe07f]HP Healed[/color] × 0.231  
            • Final CE = ([color=#ffa366]Base CE[/color] ÷ Mob Count) × (1 + [color=#ffa366]Enmity+[/color]/100)  
            • Final VE = [color=#ffa366]Final CE[/color] × 6

