                [b][u][size=16][color=#cea425]Key Insights:[/color][/size][/u][/b]
                [b][color=#F7D58B][color=#99ff99]✔[/color] With GearSwap Optimization:[/color][/b]  
                • [b]Maximized HP[/b] across all gear sets.  
                • [b]Stable HP[/b] during gear transitions.  
                • [b]Smooth swaps[/b] reduce healer strain.  
                • [b]Improved survivability[/b] in critical moments.

                [b][color=#F7D58B][color=#ff6666]✘[/color] Without GearSwap Optimization:[/color][/b]  
                • [b]Heavy HP loss[/b] during gear changes.  
                • [b]Unstable HP[/b] across transitions.  
                • [b]More healer pressure[/b].  
                • [b]Increased vulnerability[/b].

