            [div id="section-sird-enmity" style="
            margin:10px auto; 
            background-color:rgba(254, 254, 254, 0.1); 
            padding:10px; 
            border-radius:10px; 
            border:2px ridge rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5); 
            box-shadow: inset 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 1), 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);  
            color:#E0E0E0; 
            font-size:14px;
            text-align:left;"]
                [div align="center" style="text-align:center; font-size:25px; margin-bottom:15px;"][color=#cea425]SIRD Enmity Set
                    [url=#section-enmity-sets style="font-size:14px;"][color=#2980B9]▲ Back to top ▲[/color][/url][/div][table]
                    [tr][td style="color:#E0E0E0; line-height:2; font-size:14px; padding:10px;"]The [color=#66ccff]SIRD Enmity set[/color] is designed for casting longer spells (e.g. [color=#00ffd0]Geist Wall[/color], [color=#00ffd0]Sheep Song[/color], [color=#00ffd0]Blank Gaze[/color], etc.) without interruption, while remaining tanky and maximizing [color=#ff7f50]Enmity[/color].

                            • [color=#F7D58B]SIRD Cap (102%)[/color]: Ensures uninterrupted spellcasting to secure aggro.  
                            • [color=#F7D58B]PDT & MDT[/color]: Ideally, aim to cap both physical and magical damage reduction.  
                            • [color=#7fe07f]~3000 HP Pool[/color]: Maintains a healthy HP total for survivability.  
                            • [color=#ff7f50]Maximize Enmity[/color]: Boost threat without sacrificing the above stats.

                            By balancing these elements ([color=#F7D58B]SIRD[/color], [color=#F7D58B]Damage Reduction[/color], [color=#7fe07f]HP[/color], and [color=#ff7f50]Enmity[/color]), this set enables consistent casting under heavy pressure and effective threat management.
                        [/td]

                    [/tr]
                [/table][div align="center"][table style="border-collapse:collapse; padding:5px; margin-top:15px; margin-bottom:15px; line-height:1.8; box-shadow:0 0 2px rgba(255, 223, 128, 1), 0 0 4px rgba(255, 223, 128, 1), 0 0 12px rgba(255, 223, 128, 1); border-radius:25px; overflow:hidden;"]
                        [tr style="background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);"][td style="text-align:center; padding:10px; vertical-align:middle; width:130px;"][itemset]397880[/itemset][/td]
                            [td style="color:#ffffff; text-align:center; padding:10px; vertical-align:middle; white-space:nowrap;"][div style="text-align:left; display:inline-block; line-height:1.5;"][size=14]• [color=#F7D58B][b]SIRD: 105%[/b][/color][/size] [size=12][color=#F7D58B][i](5/5 SIRD Other Merits)[/i][/color][/size]
                                    [size=14]• [b][color=#F7D58B]Enmity: +114[/color][/b][/size]
                                    [size=14]• [b][color=#F7D58B]PDT: -68%[/color][/b][/size]
                                    [size=14]• [color=#F7D58B][b]MDT: -56%[/b][/color][/size] [size=12][color=#F7D58B][i](Capped with Shell)[/i][/color][/size]
                                    [size=14]• [b][color=#F7D58B]HP: +840[/color][/b][/size]
                                    [size=14]• [b][color=#F7D58B]MP: +97[/color][/b][/size]
                                    [size=14]• [b][color=#F7D58B]VIT: +213[/color][/b][/size]
                                    [size=14]• [b][color=#F7D58B]DEF: +1148[/color][/b][/size]
                                [/div]
                            [/td]
                            [td style="color:#ffffff; text-align:center; padding:10px; vertical-align:top; white-space:nowrap;"][size=12][b][color=#66ccff]Rudianos's Mantle Augments[/color][/b][/size]
                                    [size=12]• [b][color=#F7D58B]VIT: +20[/color][/b][/size]
                                    [size=12]• [b][color=#F7D58B]PDT: -10%[/color][/b][/size]
                                    [size=12]• [b][color=#F7D58B]Mag Eva: +10[/color][/b][/size]
                                    [size=12]• [b][color=#F7D58B]Eva. / Mag Eva: +20[/color][/b][/size]
                                    [size=12]• [b][color=#F7D58B]Enmity: +10[/color][/b][/size]

                                    [size=12][b][color=#66ccff]Odyssean Greaves Augments[/color][/b][/size]
                                    [size=12]• [b][color=#F7D58B]Enmity: +8 (Fern stone)[/color][/b][/size]
                            [/td]
