        [div style="margin:25px auto; background-color:rgba(26, 26, 26, 0.85); width:100%; padding:5px; border-radius:15px; border:2px ridge rgba(255, 223, 128, 1); box-shadow:0 0 10px rgba(244, 228, 142, 0.8), 0 0 5px rgba(255, 223, 0, 0.6) inset;"][div align="center" style="margin:15px 0 25px 0; padding:10px;"][img style="width:450px; height:auto;"]https://i.imgur.com/Rd4V1im.png[/img]
            [/div][div style="font-size:26px; font-weight:bold; color:#ffd700; text-shadow: 0px 0px 5px rgba(253, 108, 0, 0.5), 0px 0px 10px rgba(253, 108, 0, 0.5), 0px 0px 15px rgba(253, 108, 0, 0.5);"]FAST CAST SETS[/div]
            [url=#section-job-ability-sets style="font-size:14px;"][color=#2980B9]▲ Back to top ▲[/color][/url]
            
            [div id="section-fastcast" style="
            margin:10px auto; 
            background-color:rgba(254, 254, 254, 0.1); 
            padding:10px; 
            border-radius:10px; 
            border:2px ridge rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5); 
            box-shadow: inset 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 1), 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);  
            color:#E0E0E0; 
            font-size:14px;
            text-align:left;"][table][tr][td style="color:#E0E0E0; line-height:2; font-size:14px; padding:10px;"]The [color=#66ccff]Fast Cast Set[/color] is designed exclusively for the [color=#F7D58B]Precast[/color] phase to minimize spell casting time. This set does not impact [color=#e5d522]Job Abilities (JAs)[/color] and is solely focused on reducing the casting time of spells.
        
                            Since this set is equipped very briefly through [color=#F7D58B]Gearswap[/color], defensive stats like [color=#F7D58B]PDT[/color], [color=#F7D58B]MDT[/color], and [color=#F7D58B]DT[/color] are irrelevant. I have never noticed any unusually high damage taken during the transition into Fast Cast gear with [color=#F7D58B]Gearswap[/color].
                        
                            This set is capped at [color=#F7D58B]80% Fast Cast[/color] to achieve the shortest possible spell casting time. Although it has the lowest HP pool among all sets, it remains reasonable with [color=#7fe07f]2938 HP[/color] compared to [color=#7fe07f]3057 HP[/color] in Idle for an Elvaan.
                        
                            Showing alternative sets other than the BiS seems unnecessary for this specific purpose. However, I will still suggest other Fast Cast gear options below for those seeking a tankier setup or not using [color=#F7D58B]Gearswap[/color].
                        [/td]
                    [/tr]
                [/table]
                [div align="center"][table style="border-collapse:collapse; padding:5px; margin-top:15px; margin-bottom:15px; line-height:1.8; box-shadow:0 0 2px rgba(255, 223, 128, 1), 0 0 4px rgba(255, 223, 128, 1), 0 0 12px rgba(255, 223, 128, 1); border-radius:25px; overflow:hidden;"]
