            [url=#section-phalanx-sets style="font-size:14px;"][color=#2980B9]▲ Back to top ▲[/color][/url]
            
            [div id="section-phalanx-potency" style="
            margin:10px auto; 
            background-color:rgba(254, 254, 254, 0.1); 
            padding:10px; 
            border-radius:10px; 
            border:2px ridge rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5); 
            box-shadow: inset 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 1), 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);  
            color:#E0E0E0; 
            font-size:14px;
            text-align:left;"][div align="center" style="text-align:center; font-size:25px; margin-bottom:15px;"][color=#cea425]PHALANX POTENCY
                    [url=#section-phalanx-sets style="font-size:14px;"][color=#2980B9]▲ Back to top ▲[/color][/url][/div]
                    [table][tr][td style="color:#E0E0E0; line-height:2; font-size:14px; padding:10px;"]The [color=#66ccff]Phalanx Potency Set[/color] is designed to maximize damage reduction by stacking [color=#F7D58B]Phalanx+[/color] gear and achieving [color=#F7D58B]415 Enhancing Magic Skill[/color]. This balance ensures optimal mitigation while maintaining strong defensive stats.

                        This set is primarily used between fights to refresh [color=#F7D58B]Phalanx[/color] with maximum potency. For casting [color=#F7D58B]Phalanx[/color] during combat, it is recommended to switch to the [color=#F7D58B]Phalanx SIRD[/color] set for greater interruption resistance.

                        If losing TP is not a concern, equipping [color=#F7D58B]Sakpata's Sword[/color] and [color=#F7D58B]Priwen[/color] shield will maximize potency, bringing the total [color=#F7D58B]Phalanx[/color] bonus to +69.
                        
                        The build combines high [color=#F7D58B]Phalanx[/color] values with solid defensive stats, achieving [color=#F7D58B]PDT[/color], [color=#F7D58B]MDT[/color], and overall [color=#F7D58B]DT[/color] reduction to stay tanky even when not actively engaged in battle.
                        [/td][/tr]
                [/table][div align="center"][table style="border-collapse:collapse; padding:5px; margin-top:15px; margin-bottom:15px; line-height:1.8; box-shadow:0 0 2px rgba(255, 223, 128, 1), 0 0 4px rgba(255, 223, 128, 1), 0 0 12px rgba(255, 223, 128, 1); border-radius:25px; overflow:hidden;"]
                        [tr style="background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);"][td style="text-align:center; padding:10px; vertical-align:middle; width:130px;"][itemset]397524[/itemset][/td]
                            [td style="color:#ffffff; text-align:center; padding:10px; vertical-align:middle; white-space:nowrap;"][div style="text-align:left; display:inline-block; line-height:1.5;"][size=14]• [b][color=#F7D58B]Phalanx: +30[/color][/b][/size] [size=12][color=#F7D58B][i](Phalanx Total: 62 with Enhancing skill)[/i][/color][/size]
                                    [size=14]• [b][color=#F7D58B]Enhancing Skill: 416[/color][/b][/size] [size=12][color=#F7D58B][i](334 Base, +16 merits, +46 ML, +20 Gears)[/i][/color][/size]
                                    [size=14]• [b][color=#F7D58B]PDT: -61%[/color][/b][/size]
                                    [size=14]• [color=#F7D58B][b]MDT: -47%[/b][/color][/size] [size=12][color=#F7D58B][i](65% with Shell IV)[/i][/color][/size]
                                    [size=14]• [b][color=#F7D58B]DEF: +1138[/color][/b][/size]
                                    [size=14]• [b][color=#F7D58B]HP: +983[/color][/b][/size] [size=12][color=#F7D58B][i](3165HP Elvaan)[/i][/color][/size]
                                    [size=14]• [b][color=#F7D58B]MP: +310[/color][/b][/size]
                                [/div]
                            [/td]
                            [td style="color:#ffffff; text-align:center; padding:10px; vertical-align:top; white-space:nowrap;"][size=12][b][color=#66ccff]Weard Mantle Augments[/color][/b][/size]
                                    [size=12]• [b][color=#F7D58B]VIT: +5[/color][/b][/size]
                                    [size=12]• [b][color=#F7D58B]Phalanx: +5[/color][/b][/size]

                                    [size=12][b][color=#66ccff]Odyssean helm[/color][/b][/size]
                                    [size=12]• [b][color=#F7D58B]Phalanx: +5[/color][/b][/size]
                                    
                                    [size=12][b][color=#66ccff]Odyssean Chestplate[/color][/b][/size]
                                    [size=12]• [b][color=#F7D58B]Phalanx: +5[/color][/b][/size]
