            [div id="section-phalanx-sird" style="
            margin:10px auto; 
            background-color:rgba(254, 254, 254, 0.1); 
            padding:10px; 
            border-radius:10px; 
            border:2px ridge rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5); 
            box-shadow: inset 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 1), 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);  
            color:#E0E0E0; 
            font-size:14px;
            text-align:left;"][div align="center" style="text-align:center; font-size:25px; margin-bottom:15px;"][color=#cea425]PHALANX SIRD
                    [url=#section-phalanx-sets style="font-size:14px;"][color=#2980B9]▲ Back to top ▲[/color][/url][/div]
                    [table][tr][td style="color:#E0E0E0; line-height:2; font-size:14px; padding:10px;"]The [color=#66ccff]Phalanx SIRD Set[/color] is specifically designed for situations where casting [color=#F7D58B]Phalanx[/color] during combat is crucial such as when you've been debuffed or are solo leveling in [color=#F7D58B]Crawler's Nest [S][/color]. This setup ensures maximum [color=#F7D58B]Spell Interruption Rate Down (SIRD)[/color] to maintain uninterrupted casting under pressure, while still providing strong defense and optimal [color=#F7D58B]Phalanx Potency[/color].

                                Whenever possible, prioritize the [color=#66ccff]Phalanx Potency set[/color] between pulls, especially when teamed up with a [color=#F7D58B]Red Mage (RDM)[/color] to extend [color=#F7D58B]Phalanx[/color] duration during events. This proactive approach helps avoid situations where the SIRD set becomes necessary.
                        [/td][/tr]
                [/table][div align="center"][table style="border-collapse:collapse; padding:5px; margin-top:15px; margin-bottom:15px; line-height:1.8; box-shadow:0 0 2px rgba(255, 223, 128, 1), 0 0 4px rgba(255, 223, 128, 1), 0 0 12px rgba(255, 223, 128, 1); border-radius:25px; overflow:hidden;"]
                        [tr style="background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);"][td style="text-align:center; padding:10px; vertical-align:middle; width:130px;"][itemset]397921[/itemset][/td]
                            [td style="color:#ffffff; text-align:center; padding:10px; vertical-align:middle; white-space:nowrap;"][div style="text-align:left; display:inline-block; line-height:1.5;"][size=14]• [color=#F7D58B][b]SIRD: 106%[/b][/color][/size] [size=12][color=#F7D58B][i](5/5 SIRD Other Merits)[/i][/color][/size]
                                    [size=14]• [b][color=#F7D58B]Phalanx: +30[/color][/b][/size] [size=12][color=#F7D58B][i](Phalanx Total: 61 with Enhancing skill)[/i][/color][/size]
                                    [size=14]• [b][color=#F7D58B]Enhancing Skill: 396[/color][/b][/size] [size=12][color=#F7D58B][i](334 Base, +16 merits, +46 ML)[/i][/color][/size]
                                    [size=14]• [b][color=#F7D58B]PDT: -50%[/color][/b][/size]
                                    [size=14]• [color=#F7D58B][b]MDT: -48%[/b][/color][/size] [size=12][color=#F7D58B][i](Capped with Shell)[/i][/color][/size]
                                    [size=14]• [b][color=#F7D58B]DEF: +1044[/color][/b][/size]
