        [div style="margin:25px auto; background-color:rgba(26, 26, 26, 0.85); width:100%; padding:5px; border-radius:15px; border:2px ridge rgba(255, 223, 128, 1); box-shadow:0 0 10px rgba(244, 228, 142, 0.8), 0 0 5px rgba(255, 223, 0, 0.6) inset;"][div align="center" style="margin:15px 0 25px 0; padding:10px;"][img style="width:450px; height:auto;"]https://i.imgur.com/Rd4V1im.png[/img]
            [/div][div style="font-size:26px; font-weight:bold; color:#ffd700; text-shadow: 0px 0px 5px rgba(253, 108, 0, 0.5), 0px 0px 10px rgba(253, 108, 0, 0.5), 0px 0px 15px rgba(253, 108, 0, 0.5);"]ENHANCING SETS[/div]
            [url=#section-enhancing-sets style="font-size:14px;"][color=#2980B9]▲ Back to top ▲[/color][/url]
            
            [div id="section-enlight" style="
            margin:10px auto; 
            background-color:rgba(254, 254, 254, 0.1); 
            padding:10px; 
            border-radius:10px; 
            border:2px ridge rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5); 
            box-shadow: inset 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 1), 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);  
            color:#E0E0E0; 
            font-size:14px;
            text-align:left;"][div align="center" style="text-align:center; font-size:25px; margin-bottom:15px;"][color=#cea425]ENLIGHT II SIRD
                    [url=#section-enhancing-sets style="font-size:14px;"][color=#2980B9]▲ Back to top ▲[/color][/url][/div]
                    [table][tr][td style="color:#E0E0E0; line-height:2; font-size:14px; padding:10px;"]The [color=#66ccff]Enlight II SIRD Set[/color] is designed to maximize the damage and accuracy bonus from [color=#00ffd0]Enlight II[/color] by stacking high [color=#F7D58B]Divine Magic Skill[/color] and ensuring capped [color=#F7D58B]SIRD (Spell Interruption Rate Down)[/color]. This balance allows for optimal offensive power while maintaining strong defensive stats to safely cast during combat.

                                This set is primarily used during battles to refresh [color=#F7D58B]Enlight II[/color] without risking interruption. For situations where tanking damage is critical, it is recommended to prioritize [color=#F7D58B]PDT[/color], [color=#F7D58B]MDT[/color], and [color=#F7D58B]DT[/color] reduction alongside capped [color=#F7D58B]SIRD[/color].

                                The formula for [color=#00ffd0]Enlight II[/color] is:
                                [size=12][color=#F7D58B][i](2 × floor((Divine Magic Skill + 400) ÷ 20) + floor((Divine Magic Skill + 400) ÷ 40) + Job Points)[/i][/color][/size]

                                For example, with [color=#F7D58B]569 Divine Magic Skill[/color] and [color=#F7D58B]20 Job Points[/color], the total bonus is:
                                [size=12][color=#F7D58B][i](2 × floor((569 + 400) ÷ 20) + floor((569 + 400) ÷ 40) + 20 = +140)[/i][/color][/size]

                                This build effectively balances high [color=#00ffd0]Enlight II[/color] damage and accuracy with solid defensive stats, ensuring survivability with capped [color=#F7D58B]SIRD[/color] and strong [color=#F7D58B]PDT[/color]/[color=#F7D58B]MDT[/color]/[color=#F7D58B]DT[/color] reductions during combat.
                        [/td][/tr]
                [/table][div align="center"][table style="border-collapse:collapse; padding:5px; margin-top:15px; margin-bottom:15px; line-height:1.8; box-shadow:0 0 2px rgba(255, 223, 128, 1), 0 0 4px rgba(255, 223, 128, 1), 0 0 12px rgba(255, 223, 128, 1); border-radius:25px; overflow:hidden;"]
                        [tr style="background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);"][td style="text-align:center; padding:10px; vertical-align:middle; width:130px;"][itemset]397525[/itemset][/td]
                            [td style="color:#ffffff; text-align:center; padding:10px; vertical-align:middle; white-space:nowrap;"][div style="text-align:left; display:inline-block; line-height:1.5;"][size=14]• [color=#F7D58B][b]SIRD: 110%[/b][/color][/size] [size=12][color=#F7D58B][i](5/5 SIRD Other Merits)[/i][/color][/size]
                                    [size=14]• [b][color=#F7D58B]Enlight II Attack/Accuracy: +140[/color][/b][/size] 
                                    [size=14]• [b][color=#F7D58B]Divine Skill: 569[/color][/b][/size] 
                                    [size=14]• [b][color=#F7D58B]PDT: -60%[/color][/b][/size]
                                    [size=14]• [color=#F7D58B][b]MDT: -47%[/b][/color][/size] [size=12][color=#F7D58B][i](capped with Shell)[/i][/color][/size]
                                    [size=14]• [b][color=#F7D58B]DEF: +1099[/color][/b][/size]
                                    [size=14]• [b][color=#F7D58B]HP: +862[/color][/b][/size] [size=12][color=#F7D58B][i](3044HP Elvaan)[/i][/color][/size]
                                    [size=14]• [b][color=#F7D58B]MP: +155[/color][/b][/size]
                                [/div]
                            [/td]
                        [/tr]
                    [/table]
                [/div]
            [/div]
        [/div]

        [div style="margin:25px auto; background-color:rgba(26, 26, 26, 0.85); width:100%; padding:5px; border-radius:15px; border:2px ridge rgba(255, 223, 128, 1); box-shadow:0 0 10px rgba(244, 228, 142, 0.8), 0 0 5px rgba(255, 223, 0, 0.6) inset;"][div align="center" style="margin:15px 0 25px 0; padding:10px;"][img style="width:450px; height:auto;"]https://i.imgur.com/Rd4V1im.png[/img]
            [/div][div style="font-size:26px; font-weight:bold; color:#ffd700; text-shadow: 0px 0px 5px rgba(253, 108, 0, 0.5), 0px 0px 10px rgba(253, 108, 0, 0.5), 0px 0px 15px rgba(253, 108, 0, 0.5);"]CURE SETS[/div]
            [url=#section-cure-sets style="font-size:14px;"][color=#2980B9]▲ Back to top ▲[/color][/url]
            
            [div id="section-cure-self" style="
            margin:10px auto; 
            background-color:rgba(254, 254, 254, 0.1); 
            padding:10px; 
            border-radius:10px; 
            border:2px ridge rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5); 
            box-shadow: inset 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 1), 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);  
            color:#E0E0E0; 
            font-size:14px;
            text-align:left;"][div align="center" style="text-align:center; font-size:25px; margin-bottom:15px;"][color=#cea425]CURE SELF
                    [url=#section-cure-sets style="font-size:14px;"][color=#2980B9]▲ Back to top ▲[/color][/url][/div]
                    [table][tr][td style="color:#E0E0E0; line-height:2; font-size:14px; padding:10px;"]The [color=#66ccff]Cure Self Set[/color] is designed to optimize self-healing by maximizing HP during midcast compared to precast, ensuring the highest possible recovery. For example: [color=#F7D58B]Precast.FastCast[/color] at 2938 HP transitions into [color=#F7D58B]Midcast.Cure_Self[/color] at 4160 HP, allowing powerful self-healing during combat.

                                This set incorporates both Cure Potency I and the default +25% Cure Potency II granted by [color=#e5d522]Majesty[/color], ensuring strong healing efficiency. It also maintains [color=#F7D58B]SIRD (Spell Interruption Rate Down)[/color] at 101%, which has proven sufficient to avoid interruptions with this exact configuration. However, caution is advised if you alter any [color=#F7D58B]SIRD[/color] pieces, as 101% can be unreliable depending on the gear used. A safer benchmark is 102% SIRD to guarantee consistent performance.

                                In addition to maximizing healing, this set prioritizes tankiness by balancing strong defensive stats such as [color=#F7D58B]PDT[/color], [color=#F7D58B]MDT[/color], and [color=#F7D58B]DT[/color] reductions, ensuring survivability during combat while casting self-heals.
                        [/td][/tr]
                [/table][div align="center"][table style="border-collapse:collapse; padding:5px; margin-top:15px; margin-bottom:15px; line-height:1.8; box-shadow:0 0 2px rgba(255, 223, 128, 1), 0 0 4px rgba(255, 223, 128, 1), 0 0 12px rgba(255, 223, 128, 1); border-radius:25px; overflow:hidden;"]
                        [tr style="background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);"][td style="text-align:center; padding:10px; vertical-align:middle; width:130px;"][itemset]397527[/itemset][/td]
                            [td style="color:#ffffff; text-align:center; padding:10px; vertical-align:middle; white-space:nowrap;"][div style="text-align:left; display:inline-block; line-height:1.5;"][size=14]• [color=#F7D58B][b]SIRD: 101%[/b][/color][/size] [size=12][color=#F7D58B][i](5/5 SIRD Other Merits)[/i][/color][/size]
                                    [size=14]• [b][color=#F7D58B]Cure Potency: +29%[/color][/b][/size] [size=12][color=#F7D58B][i](54% With Majesty)[/i][/color][/size]
                                    [size=14]• [b][color=#F7D58B]Healing Magic Skill: 435[/color][/b][/size] 
                                    [size=14]• [b][color=#F7D58B]PDT: -60%[/color][/b][/size]
                                    [size=14]• [color=#F7D58B][b]MDT: -49%[/b][/color][/size] [size=12][color=#F7D58B][i](capped with Shell)[/i][/color][/size]
                                    [size=14]• [b][color=#F7D58B]DEF: +1208[/color][/b][/size]
                                    [size=14]• [b][color=#F7D58B]HP: +1978[/color][/b][/size] [size=12][color=#F7D58B][i](4160HP Elvaan)[/i][/color][/size]
                                    [size=14]• [b][color=#F7D58B]MP: +111[/color][/b][/size]
                                    [size=14]• [b][color=#00ffd0]Cure III[/color] for: [color=#7fe07f]765HP[/color][/b][/size]
                                    [size=14]• [b][color=#00ffd0]Cure IV[/color] for: [color=#7fe07f]1222HP[/color][/b][/size]
                                [/div]
                            [/td]
                        [/tr]
                    [/table]
                [/div]
            [/div]

            [div id="section-cure-other" style="
            margin:10px auto; 
            background-color:rgba(254, 254, 254, 0.1); 
            padding:10px; 
            border-radius:10px; 
            border:2px ridge rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5); 
            box-shadow: inset 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 1), 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);  
            color:#E0E0E0; 
            font-size:14px;
            text-align:left;"][div align="center" style="text-align:center; font-size:25px; margin-bottom:15px;"][color=#cea425]CURE OTHER
                    [url=#section-cure-sets style="font-size:14px;"][color=#2980B9]▲ Back to top ▲[/color][/url][/div]
                    [table][tr][td style="color:#E0E0E0; line-height:2; font-size:14px; padding:10px;"]The [color=#66ccff]Cure Other Set[/color] is designed to optimize healing for other players by focusing on efficiency and reliability, without the need for a large HP pool during midcast. The set ensures seamless transitions between [color=#F7D58B]Precast.FastCast[/color] and [color=#F7D58B]Midcast.Cure_Other[/color], prioritizing consistent performance.

                                This set incorporates both Cure Potency I and the default +25% Cure Potency II granted by [color=#e5d522]Majesty[/color], ensuring efficient and potent healing. It also maintains a [color=#F7D58B]SIRD (Spell Interruption Rate Down)[/color] of 111%, which guarantees immunity to interruptions caused by physical damage during casting.

                                While this set does not focus on maximizing HP, it maintains strong defensive stats, including [color=#F7D58B]PDT[/color], [color=#F7D58B]MDT[/color], and [color=#F7D58B]DT[/color] reductions, to ensure survivability while healing allies during combat.
                        [/td][/tr]
